 Staked JELLY/WETH BPT 

##Staking NFT 
This NFT represents Staked JELLY/WETH BPT in the Zen Pool, part of the Jelly Farming program. When it is bought or sold, the value of the staked position is transferred to the new owner. 

##Zen Pool 
The Zen Pool is where $JELLY farming rewards are earnt.  

##NFT holders 
This NFT can be traded freely on the secondary market like any other NFT, you can also transfer it to a vault to keep your staked LPs safe. The NFT was minted at the time LP tokens were staked. Any wallet holding this NFT gets access to Claim the rewards and Unstake the LP tokens. A wallet can hold multiple NFTs from the same pool and these display on the Jelly protocol UI as a cumulative staked balance of LPs. 

##Jelly Farming 
 Claim, Stake and Unstake from the Jelly Pools using Jelly Protocol at [https://app.jelly.io/farms/0x59218ab7E20F824d3229E21554b7f505f6b334f3](https://app.jelly.io/farms/0x59218ab7E20F824d3229E21554b7f505f6b334f3)
